---
import casee from "../../assets/case.png";
import arrow from "../../assets/black-arrow.png";
---

<section
  class="flex flex-col px-4 sm:px-8 lg:px-20 items-center gap-y-14 py-14"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
    <h1 class="text-[32px] sm:text-[48px] lg:text-[64px]">
      Case <span class="text-primaryorange">Studies</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-center text-base">
      Explore some of our standout projects, each representing a unique facet of
      our video editing and storytelling expertise. These projects transcend
      mere videos; they're captivating narratives that inspire and make an
      impact.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="flex flex-col bg-white p-8 gap-y-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
          <!-- <img src={casee.src} class="w-[50px]" alt="" /> -->
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold">Wanderlust Chronicles</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="text-base">
            The project garnered over 1 million views and sparked a 20% increase
            in travel bookings for our client
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button
        class="flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border w-fit font-extrabold text-base border-[#98A2B3] gap-x-3 px-5 py-4"
        >View All Projects <img src={arrow.src} alt="arrow-icon" /></button
      >
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col bg-white p-8 gap-y-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
          <!-- <img src={casee.src} class="w-[50px]" alt="" /> -->
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold">City Vibes Unveiled</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="text-base">
            The series achieved a 30% increase in viewer engagement, with viewers expressing a strong connection to the featured cities.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button
        class="flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border w-fit font-extrabold text-base border-[#98A2B3] gap-x-3 px-5 py-4"
        >View All Projects <img src={arrow.src} alt="arrow-icon" /></button
      >
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col bg-white p-8 gap-y-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
          <!-- <img src={casee.src} class="w-[50px]" alt="" /> -->
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold">A Lifetime in a Day</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="text-base">
            The video left a lasting impression, with heartfelt reactions from viewers and 50,000 shares across social media platforms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button
        class="flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border w-fit font-extrabold text-base border-[#98A2B3] gap-x-3 px-5 py-4"
        >View All Projects <img src={arrow.src} alt="arrow-icon" /></button
      >
    </div>

    <div class="hidden sm:flex lg:hidden flex-col bg-white p-8 gap-y-12">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-2">
            <!-- <img src={casee.src} class="w-[50px]" alt="" /> -->
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold">Wanderlust Chronicles</p>
          </div>
  
          <div>
            <p class="text-base">
              The project garnered over 1 million views and sparked a 20% increase
              in travel bookings for our client
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <button
          class="flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border w-fit font-extrabold text-base border-[#98A2B3] gap-x-3 px-5 py-4"
          >View All Projects <img src={arrow.src} alt="arrow-icon" /></button
        >
      </div>
  
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    background: var(--gray-300, #f2f4f7);
  }
</style>
